Install command for gm-skill is `bun x skills add AnEntrypoint/gm -y` with NO -g/global flag. The skills CLI (PromptScript backend) rejects global skill installation: error "PromptScript does not support global skill installation". The -g flag was wrongly documented in README.md, site/content/pages/home.yaml, and docs/distribution.html; removed across all. The separate `bun add -g gm-skill` npm-package global install path is legitimate and unrelated. Install slug canonicalized to AnEntrypoint/gm (the legacy AnEntrypoint/gm-skill mirror slug was also corrected in home.yaml/distribution.html).